Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.36,Utama,Kaede,0,0,0,,Jangan, Mie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.40,Utama,Kaede,0,0,0,,Kau harus sabar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.44,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Segigitan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.90,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Segigitan saja, deh ....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.65,Utama,Kaede,0,0,0,,Bertahanlah!
