Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.62,Utama,Kaede,0,0,0,,Kau tak perlu memakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:07.11,Utama,Kaede,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:08.83,Utama,Kaede,0,0,0,,Aku membuatmu pusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.65,Miring,Kaede,0,0,0,,Aku pengen lenyap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:13.34,Utama,Kaede,0,0,0,,Me-Mending kubawa pulang saja, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:22.35,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Biar aku makan.
